{"tid":2498781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場： 政府開始在各區貼「竹林」「楓樹」貼紙    遮文宣、「連儂牆」","createTime":"2021-04-21T11:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T13:43:45.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"28b7f2352376a0a98a6d2067a511d06382c397f4","tid":2498781,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:36:55.000Z","msg":"【各區貼「竹林」「楓樹」貼紙    遮文宣、「連儂牆」？】<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺、西環等區的隧道或天穚橋柱，近日被發現貼上大型「竹林」「楓樹」貼紙，懷疑用作遮蔽有關前年反修例運動的文宣或「連儂牆」。《立場》向民政署查詢有關工程的用意、費用及牽涉全港多少地區等，民政署其後以電話回覆指相關工程由路政署負責。《立場》已向路政署查詢，正待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺馬會道行人隧道相片由Spark &bull; 撻著 提供<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU9CMcyyAjNtFk6YNmRFNdhn7nKTHfycjmTWGi5Jjmj9j?filename=JdF9YAf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJdF9YAf.jpg&h=1e6f5d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4094640647288191/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F4094640647288191%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=6ac153c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4094640647288191/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"c3776a24500d88dee2320535c69b8326c7b3528a","tid":2498781,"uid":133319,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"好耐啦"},{"pid":"4050d2f4512ebecf3c8e39c6fda7983fa7d9fe16","tid":2498781,"uid":916,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:43:43.000Z","msg":"貼樹貼竹會唔會又係風水野？"},{"pid":"6d592c13c7f5f023858618b251ac02ea29955de0","tid":2498781,"uid":384590,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"咁咪幾好"},{"pid":"a25c96a2ebd5f4bf8f0b7f21a3664b0605712508","tid":2498781,"uid":98431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"粉飾太平 金玉其外"},{"pid":"1640a443b7a8353f6056ad4935ac51bdb71a93ca","tid":